Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.53,P4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,148)}血型：A型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.53,P4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,198)}星座：金牛座
